A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Local Education Agencies – Educator Screening – NASDTEC Clearinghouse
3 (School Personnel Vetting and Hiring Transparency Act)
4 FOR the purpose of requiring each local education agency in the State to become an
5 associate member of the National Association of State Directors of Teacher
6 Education and Certification to utilize the Educator Identification Clearinghouse for
7 screening educators and individuals who apply to be educators; and generally
8 relating to the hiring and screening process for educators employed within local
9 school systems in the State.
